    <item>
      <title>就业数据疲软加大美联储降息压力 债券市场飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/treasury-two-year-yields-fall-to-14-month-low-on-fed-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五一份报告显示就业增长上月大幅放缓，随后债券市场反弹加剧，进一步引发人们对美联储将开始大幅降息以防止经济停滞的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/treasury-two-year-yields-fall-to-14-month-low-on-fed-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 00:41:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业加剧“增长恐慌” 股市抛售加剧：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[疲软的就业报告引发了人们对美联储降息速度过慢、可能导致经济放缓加剧的担忧，导致股市抛售加剧，债券收益率暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 22:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
